<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Feverous" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Feverous,</orth> feverish, affected with a fever: <cit><quote>a f. pulse,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 3.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 2, 38</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as if the world were f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.4.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 4, 61</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 66</bibl>. Figuratively: <cit><quote>a f. life,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 1, 75</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>